text: aryanc403 , You always were an inspiration for me when it came to competitive Programming. Wishing u all the very best for future endeavours. Aise hi chaapte rehna
author: Skand Rajmeet Upadhyay

text:
Hi shashi,
For me you were the most dependable person in the wing. Auur ESC201, me subah aake encoder, decoder padhane ke liye thanks. TA201 auur 202 kaa endsem tumhare bharose nikla tha. Koi course common hot tha toh yeh vishwas rehta tha ki Shashi bhai se pucch lunga jo kuch nahi samagh me aayega. Aise hi bhavishya me chaapte rehna...
author: Skand Rajmeet Upadhyay

text: Auur suhail bhai , badminton auur cricket bada mast khelte the , Dream11 ke team banane ke Chief strategist auur promoter the. BTW maine abhi tak Game of Thrones nahi dekha hai . Aise hi mast rho auur chaapte rho , phir milenge kabhi
author: Skand Rajmeet Upadhyay
